<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，传来了大大的喇叭声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王室信使！”继母大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继母和她的女儿们跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘用围裙擦了擦手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她跟着她们跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很好奇是什么消息。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面有一大群人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王室信使坐在马上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿着一张长纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咳咳！”信使说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个非常重要的消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子要举行一个舞会，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邀请王国里所有的淑女参加。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”几个姑娘立刻说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘的继姐姐们高兴地鼓起掌来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去参加王子舞会！”格特喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特鲁迪的眼睛亮了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太令人兴奋了！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许王子会向我求婚！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格特哼了一声：“不可能，特鲁迪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子会爱上我的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我又美又高。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特鲁迪把手放在屁股上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我很漂亮，而且丰满！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“姑娘们，姑娘们。”继母说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们两个都很漂亮。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果是舞会。”灰姑娘轻声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“会有音乐和舞蹈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定很有趣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！灰姑娘！”继母放声大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不可能去舞会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为你不是淑女！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>